STEP 1: Check node installation COMMAND: node -v if it is installed then it
shows you a version of node like v18.16.0
 STEP 2: create 2 files index.html
style.css 
STEP 3: Check directory TAILWIND\Lecture 21.. you can go in directory
by using cd .\TAILWIND\ cd '.\Lecture 21' 
STEP 4: COMMAND: npm init -y "create
package.json" 
STEP 5: go to documentation and copy COMMAND: npm install -D
tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer "create node_modules and package-lock.json"
STEP 6: go to documentation and copy COMMAND: npx tailwindcss init -p "create
postcss.config.js , tailwind.config.js" 
STEP 7: go to file tailwind.config.js
and edit content:["*"] 
STEP 8: go to style.css and paste @tailwind base;
@tailwind components; @tailwind utilities; go to index.html and paste
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />

STEP 9: npm i vite Step 10: package.json edit "scripts": { "dev": "vite" }, STEP
11: npm run dev
